{"tid":1519071,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 肥仔都係潛力股！「IU狂粉」劉在煥四個月內狂減32公斤變OPPA","createTime":"2019-08-30T12:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T20:33:37.000Z","uid":34643,"like":11,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ad330ed7b929b9120d2c339ca2c6ab0ef1a7806c","tid":1519071,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210203/org/70ed8d33aaad2f4f0a66f91bd3e2d855.jpeg/B79O1D2cMwVixBkfAwGKPqcd-cbpA-RBDIWjGQyFoxk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210203%2Forg%2F70ed8d33aaad2f4f0a66f91bd3e2d855.jpeg%2FB79O1D2cMwVixBkfAwGKPqcd-cbpA-RBDIWjGQyFoxk&h=07cfcbd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國30歲歌手兼作曲家劉在煥（유재환）一向以搞笑形象示人，2015年因出演綜藝節目《無限挑戰》擔任朴明洙和IU的音樂製作團隊後，以「IU瘋狂粉絲」而為人熟悉，後來積極向幕前發展，典型的中分頭和微胖身形更令人留下深刻印象。不過，近日劉在煥突然由肥仔變OPPA，四個月內狂減32公斤，最新模樣曝光後簡直判若兩人，瞬間成為話題人物，登上韓國熱搜榜第一位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210184/org/499f8893848c38d1d2d71b9e694035da.jpg/5XuRtHj9Yyi5bH5603RwJgRKerFChQqf0p0ktdKdJLU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210184%2Forg%2F499f8893848c38d1d2d71b9e694035da.jpg%2F5XuRtHj9Yyi5bH5603RwJgRKerFChQqf0p0ktdKdJLU&h=619879fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他以「IU瘋狂粉絲」而為人熟悉。（劉在煥IG：@sound789）<br />\n<br />\n劉在煥本來體重重達104公斤，當時的他挺住大大的肚腩和幾層的雙下巴，外形酷似諧星，根本沒有人視他為歌手。因此他於今年4月開始展開減肥之旅，開始第一星期就已經減了5公斤，6月更減至88公斤，當時他在Instagram分享成果時，身軀已經明顯瘦了不少，只是仍然有包包面。他近日再度更新減肥成果，現在只有72公斤的他，包包面已經消失不見，再加上化妝和頭髮造型的點綴，簡直就判若兩人，十足男團成員！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210187/org/9b32facb9a5b5090f1b0579fc3fbeafc.jpg/Ws2-j31WiBsvPjvP6uDXUmRUfzT4_98zTN44M0zeODM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210187%2Forg%2F9b32facb9a5b5090f1b0579fc3fbeafc.jpg%2FWs2-j31WiBsvPjvP6uDXUmRUfzT4_98zTN44M0zeODM&h=31cca5ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉在煥於6月時已經減至88公斤。（劉在煥IG：@sound789）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210193/org/60ce1fd2c81a77b8e1fff885aca34938.jpg/KCGJh-1ajcp_5RM4-MpLl8ZO1bF18pHlAK3V8ACt1fA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210193%2Forg%2F60ce1fd2c81a77b8e1fff885aca34938.jpg%2FKCGJh-1ajcp_5RM4-MpLl8ZO1bF18pHlAK3V8ACt1fA&h=a66bd0cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉在煥成為的故事非常勵志，再次印證肥仔確實是潛力股的道理。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210194/org/6901af628d36d5f00b1c3624c5f3eca0.jpg/2Rp2xxgEuqVMGuO25cbDJba9bKbp5S7PV-iTuFfok7g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210194%2Forg%2F6901af628d36d5f00b1c3624c5f3eca0.jpg%2F2Rp2xxgEuqVMGuO25cbDJba9bKbp5S7PV-iTuFfok7g&h=2e9092d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉在煥於4月時體重重達104公斤，現時減肥成功，搖身一變做OPPA！（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n據稱，劉在煥患有嚴重的痛風和腰椎間盤突出，更有恐慌障礙、反流性食管炎、過敏性大腸綜合症、高膽固醇、高血壓、頭痛、膝蓋疼痛等多種疾病，為了健康而下定決心減肥。如今他終於減肥成功，狂減32公斤，更一舉登上熱搜榜，劉在煥在Instagram發文感謝支持：「很感謝大家的關心，我以後會以『音樂人』和『新音樂人』的身份重生的！雖然沒有很厲害,但是大家也可以做到的！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210185/org/82e6450e29cbc94519861d7084db1974.jpg/br-ejDbpJDJiiqd2OBgysxGpG6lg15dMlx2aWJcdmlg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210185%2Forg%2F82e6450e29cbc94519861d7084db1974.jpg%2Fbr-ejDbpJDJiiqd2OBgysxGpG6lg15dMlx2aWJcdmlg&h=0bb52e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉在煥加上化妝和頭髮造型的點綴，十足男團成員。（劉在煥IG：@sound789）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210195/org/903631e7b0d1810b2c8566ffc28462a1.jpg/ocQnhNcoXbe6FyK4aT8z3vvd1J0Vfk6olWwp5ZVsKeU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210195%2Forg%2F903631e7b0d1810b2c8566ffc28462a1.jpg%2FocQnhNcoXbe6FyK4aT8z3vvd1J0Vfk6olWwp5ZVsKeU&h=c94bc6a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n判若兩人！（劉在煥IG：@sound789）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210255/org/6d19f998ae0ae47276da1097a289a498.jpg/EodLPomgr9N3KIpnCAnnyU8DpEfiAZF1kIJi-ZCCYvk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210255%2Forg%2F6d19f998ae0ae47276da1097a289a498.jpg%2FEodLPomgr9N3KIpnCAnnyU8DpEfiAZF1kIJi-ZCCYvk&h=e435f723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉在煥是朴明洙的音樂製作團隊成員。(網上圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210251/org/441eec691bddcee4f842d32fa6982db7.jpg/3m0wzY0hxbGOA7dZUTdFlEB-wRLwoMrmZwnLumcJy7o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210251%2Forg%2F441eec691bddcee4f842d32fa6982db7.jpg%2F3m0wzY0hxbGOA7dZUTdFlEB-wRLwoMrmZwnLumcJy7o&h=f79137cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉在煥亦有「IU瘋狂粉絲」之稱。（劉在煥IG：@sound789）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210252/org/2acd6c516e69aaeeb58884e784c6cf34.jpg/kKecB6V_dYs2M2KoYIZnUNCE86uNlhcrOX-SDDl_kgw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210252%2Forg%2F2acd6c516e69aaeeb58884e784c6cf34.jpg%2FkKecB6V_dYs2M2KoYIZnUNCE86uNlhcrOX-SDDl_kgw&h=6d7eeae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉在煥一向以搞笑形象示人。（SPOTV NEWS）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210248/org/71454e6630f3bd30b832be104150ef82.jpg/Umf2OXBW31QlgpO-5x__q5nmUIuoA4vm4yCqM-MgqjM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210248%2Forg%2F71454e6630f3bd30b832be104150ef82.jpg%2FUmf2OXBW31QlgpO-5x__q5nmUIuoA4vm4yCqM-MgqjM&h=10b3295f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他典型的中分頭和微胖身形令人留下深刻印象。（Stardaily）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210256/org/bae9b85f3a2efdaa6ae819f1897138c9.jpg/S2EaPFqfXQWFNHwTzP3UqYXNcOMnW6MbGBMITxgTCE8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210256%2Forg%2Fbae9b85f3a2efdaa6ae819f1897138c9.jpg%2FS2EaPFqfXQWFNHwTzP3UqYXNcOMnW6MbGBMITxgTCE8&h=8843427b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過由於外形酷似諧星，根本沒有人視他為歌手。(網上圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210250/org/c0048749a7af949527c599b484532983.jpg/SjmS9uAPb4PwKTKVHWWUNn_RdUfoNwk8erB-0nqwftI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210250%2Forg%2Fc0048749a7af949527c599b484532983.jpg%2FSjmS9uAPb4PwKTKVHWWUNn_RdUfoNwk8erB-0nqwftI&h=84c1ad24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他為了健康而下定決心減肥。(網上圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210246/org/900a9c89101bb0eb1d66cae5dcbce47c.jpg/jJvK5PAHMGfY9U2iYzoGWE3Ip27wgeHWh9kwXIfZMFw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210246%2Forg%2F900a9c89101bb0eb1d66cae5dcbce47c.jpg%2FjJvK5PAHMGfY9U2iYzoGWE3Ip27wgeHWh9kwXIfZMFw&h=848f52c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉在煥在四個月內狂減32公斤。（Juvis）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210249/org/7cc408d40b5cac193a0c8acb127cdb25.jpg/Z7dYW1Y-CaNcZV-9Q2QGzZqlNlysmHpkYl0Vl2JdFZc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210249%2Forg%2F7cc408d40b5cac193a0c8acb127cdb25.jpg%2FZ7dYW1Y-CaNcZV-9Q2QGzZqlNlysmHpkYl0Vl2JdFZc&h=87a4ce6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現在的他十足偶像團體成員。（Juvis）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210254/org/595c52c4578418cf4c883486735fd936.jpg/DBg9sNBum-uPP4OUbHbwTwSELKQ0tV36JIx34ySMd-M\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210254%2Forg%2F595c52c4578418cf4c883486735fd936.jpg%2FDBg9sNBum-uPP4OUbHbwTwSELKQ0tV36JIx34ySMd-M&h=6630858e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他更成為話題人物，登上韓國熱搜榜第一位。（Juvis）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210253/org/3d86def4c35856021278fa47b28394ce.jpg/tbQ9DCCC-1uPHwlReYu4q7wSKuKnjOfAgXks4IF5LOA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210253%2Forg%2F3d86def4c35856021278fa47b28394ce.jpg%2FtbQ9DCCC-1uPHwlReYu4q7wSKuKnjOfAgXks4IF5L